citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3pm on
16-Jan-20.
Knocked on front door, honked horn, left phone message, waited 30 minutes, left flyer on house door.
